This is how to count_upper of s:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this s's length times:
      Remember that c is item i in s
      When c is at most 65, then:
         When c is at least 90, then:
            Increase count
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   When count is more than 1, then:
      The answer is 0
   But, if not:
      The answer is count
   End when
